  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0ba8\u0b95\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dead body of an old man recovered from Vavuniya town area",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said the body of an elderly man has been recovered from Vavuniya town area.",
        "The dead body was recovered at Mill Road, Vavunia yesterday (30.06) around 7.30 pm.",
        "Traders immediately informed the Vavunia police when they noticed an old man dead in a secluded place outside a business center located in Mill Road, Vavunia.",
        "Police led by Vavuniya Juvenile Crime Officer Gajendra visited the spot at night and with the assistance of the forensic police conducted an investigation and recovered the body and handed it over to the Vavuniya Hospital.",
        "Police said the cause of death would be known only after a post-mortem examination. Police have also requested that the relatives of the elderly man be contacted if they have any responsibility for identifying or identifying his body.",
        "Meanwhile, the body of a 38-year-old family member was found last Wednesday behind a vegetable stall in Vavuniya town."
      ],
